ActGeneral Campaign Star and General Service Medal Regulations, 2009
SubjectOrder Awarding of the General Service Medal with a SOUTH-WEST ASIA ribbon
PrecisOrder (a) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2004-756 of June 17, 2004; (b) determining who has rendered service that is worthy of recognition by the award of the General Service Medal with the SOUTH-WEST ASIA ribbon; and (c) establishing its order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
